OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA brighter but breezy day on
OL,6,FWednesday with a mix of cloud and
OL,7,Fsunny spells. A few showers possible,
OL,8,Fespecially across the north of the
OL,9,Fregion. Temperatures near normal.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLargely dry this evening with
OL,12,Fcloud building from the west. Turning
OL,13,Fwidely windy overnight especially over
OL,14,Fthe hills with some patchy rain by
OL,15,Fdawn. Frost-free overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
