OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA very windy day with gales
OL,6,Fin places. Often cloudy with rain,
OL,7,Flocally heavy in places, sinking
OL,8,Fsouthwards across the region followed
OL,9,Fby showers, wintry over the hills.
OL,10,FTurning colder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,13,Fon Friday with blustery heavy showers,
OL,14,Foccasionally wintry, especially in the
OL,15,Fnorth. Drier and less cold on
OL,16,FSaturday. Then further rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
